<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.10">
<l>yāmaṭa lūrntu memmāḻi yaṅkaip pirāṉuṭai</l>
<l>tūmaṭa ṟaṇṇan tuḻāymalar koṇṭu cūṭuvō</l>
<l>māmaṭa miṉṟit teruvu tōṟaya ṟaiyalār</l>
<l>nāmaṭaṅ kappaḻi tūṟṟi nāṭu miraikkavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We would mount the palmyra stem. We would take [and] wear</l>
<l>the cool Tulsi blossoms with pure fronds of our lord, discus in [his] palm</l>
<l>while, without the ignorance that is there, on every street the neighbour women’s</l>
<l>tongues will be wagged [and] the land will cry out, casting blame.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
